des:
You'll get all kinds of music on Jack FM 92.5. You'll hear most of your favorite 80's rock and pop hits as well as rock and pop hits of the 70s, 90s and 00s.
Once enabled, just say: "Alexa, open ninety two point five jack f. m." and Alexa will guide you from there!
